The paper deals with 3D face reconstruction and recognition using deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for regression also suggests that the paper may fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses generating labeled examples, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM).
